0candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20108%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20have%20increased%20which%20needs%20111%20to%20send%20all%20its%20three%20candidates%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20two%20Congress%20MLAs%2C%20the%20party%20will%20be%20one%20vote%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lone%20BSP%20MLA%20Uma%20Shankar%20Singh%20has%20not%20made%20his%20inclinations%20clear%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20to%20take%20on%20sitting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsonia-gandhi-moves-to-rajya-sabha-as-congress-names-8-candidates-for-upper-house-polls%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mahajan%20who%20was%20considered%20close%20to%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20left%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%202022.%20The%20Congress%20has%2040%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20assembly%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20and%203%20are%20independent%20MLAs.%20The%20saffron%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20cross%20voting%20may%20help%20get%20Mahajan%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20high%20chance%20of%20cross-voting%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbanking-on-discontent-within-the-ruling-congress-bjp-fields-a-rajya-sabha-candidate-from-himachal-pradesh%2Farticle67849015.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinghvi%E2%80%99s%20candidature%20from%20the%20state%20has%20upset%20a%20section%20of%20the%20party%2C%20after%20he%20was%20chosen%20over%20former%20union%20minister%20Anand%20Sharma%2C%20a%20party%20veteran%20from%20the%20state.%20Singhvi%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20is%20the%20first%20since%201952%20that%20a%20non-Himachali