o%20him%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20moved%20a%20trust%20vote%20in%20the%20Assembly%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20on%20the%20motion%20will%20be%20held%20tomorrow%2C%20a%20day%20on%20which%20the%20AAP%20chief%20is%20also%20supposed%20to%20appear%20before%20a%20court%20and%20explain%20why%20he%20had%20skipped%20the%20five%20earlier%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20the%20vote%20of%20confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20two%20AAP%20MLAs%20told%20him%20that%20they%20were%20approached%20by%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20who%20claimed%20that%20the%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20would%20be%20arrested%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MLAs%20were%20told%20that%2021%20AAP%20legislators%20have%20agreed%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20and%20more%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20BJP.%20They%20offered%20the%20MLAs%20Rs%2025%20crore%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%20The%20MLAs%20told%20me%20they%20did%20not%20accept.%20When%20we%20spoke%20to%20other%20MLAs%2C%20we%20found%20that%20they%20had%20not%20contacted%2021%2C%20but%20seven.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20carry%20out%20another%20Operation%20Lotus%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20is%20not%20a%20scam%20at%20all%20but%20an%20attempt%20to%20break%20our%20party%20and%20topple%20the%20government%20by%20filing%20false%20cases%20like%20they%20have%20in%20other%20states.%20Their%20aim%20is%20not%20to%20carry%20out%20an%20investigation%20but%20to%20arrest%20our%20leaders%20-%20and%20they%20have%20already%20arrested%20some%20-%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20Their%20aim%20is%20to%20topple%20the%20government%20because%20they%20know%20they%20can%20never%20win%20elections%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20chief%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20form%20its%20own%20government%20in%20Delhi%20by%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20god's%20grace%20and%20thanks%20to%20people's%20faith%20in%20us%2C%20they%20were%20unsuccessful.%20So%2C%20to%20see%20for%20ourselves%20and%20show%20the%20people%20that%20not%20one%20of%20our%20MLAs%20defected%20and%20all%20of%20them%20are%20with%20us%2C%20I%20am%20presenting%20a%20motion%20of%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%2062%20MLAs%20in%20the%2070-member%20Assembly%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20eight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETomorrow's%20trust%20vote%2C%20which%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20being%20served%20notices%20by%20the%20crime%20branch%20over%20their%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoach%26quot%3B%20AAP%20MLAs%2C%20will%20be%20the%20party's%20second%20in%20two%20years.%20After%20making%20similar%20allegations%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20trying%20to%20topple%20its%20government%2C%20the%20party%20had%20tabled%2C%20and%20won%2C%20a%20confidence%20motion%20in%202022%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20Troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20its%20sixth%20summons%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20agency%20for%20questioning%20on%20Monday%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20chief%20has%20skipped%20five%20summons%20so%20far%20and%20he%20and%20his%20party%20have%20repeatedly%20claimed%20that%20the%20summonses%20were%20illegal%20and%20the%20agency's%20only%20aim%20is%20to%20arrest%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%203%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20skipped%20the%20fifth%20summons%2C%20the%20ED%20also%20moved%20th