20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20reported%20by%20PTI%20earlier%20that%20the%20BCCI%20will%20be%20making%20it%20mandatory%20for%20Indian%20players%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20Ranji%20trophy%20for%20at%20least%20three%20or%20four%20matches%20in%20case%20they%20wish%20to%20play%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20informed%20on%20phone%20already%20and%20I'm%20going%20to%20write%20letters%20as%20well%20that%20if%20your%20chairman%20of%20selectors%2C%20your%20coach%20and%20your%20captain%20are%20asking%20for%20it%20then%20you%20will%20have%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20it%20was%20to%20happen%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20guidance%20from%20the%20national%20cricket%20Academy%20in%20Bangalore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20advice%20we%20get%20from%20the%20NCA%20%E2%80%94%20say%20suppose%20somebody's%20body%20is%20not%20able%20to%20handle%20both%20white-ball%20and%20red-ball%20cricket%20%E2%80%94%20so%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20impose%20anything%20in%20that%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(It%20applies%20to)%20whoever%20is%20fit%20and%20young%20%E2%80%94%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20tolerate%20any%20other%20tantrums.%20This%20message%20is%20for%20all%20centrally%20contracted%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shah%20providing%20further%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20otherwise%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20given%20me%20his%20suggestions%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20let%20him%20take%20his%20own%20calls%20freely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708086360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Flsnmb4g8_rohit-jay-shah-asia-cup_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%