%20This%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20engage%20targets%20that%20are%20beyond%20the%20visual%20line%20of%20sight%20in%20the%20tactical%20battle%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Air%20Defence%20Systems%20will%20be%20strengthened%20with%20the%20new%20tactical%20control%20radars%20capable%20of%20detecting%20slow%2C%20small%2C%20and%20low-flying%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedium%20Range%20Maritime%20Reconnaissance%20and%20Multi-Mission%20Maritime%20Aircraft%20will%20be%20procured%20to%20strengthen%20the%20surveillance%20and%20interdiction%20capabilities%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20and%20neutralize%20targets%20underwater%2C%20Active%20Towed%20Array%20Sonar%20and%20heavy-weight%20torpedoes%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20brought%20in.%20These%20acquisitions%20will%20enhance%20the%20detection%20and%20attacking%20capabilities%20of%20naval%20assets%2C%20particularly%20the%20Kalvari%20Class%20submarines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20council%20has%20also%20given%20the%20green%20light%20for%20the%20procurement%20of%20Flight%20Refueller%20Aircraft%20to%20augment%20the%20operational%20capabilities%20and%20reach%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20The%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20get%20new%20software-defined%20radios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20the%20role%20of%20start-ups%20and%20MSMEs%20in%20fostering%20innovation%2C%20the%20council%20has%20introduced%20amendments%20to%20the%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Procedure%20(DAP)%202020.%20These%20changes%2C%20focusing%20on%20benchmarking%2C%20cost%20computation%2C%20payment%20schedules%2C%20and%20procurement%20quantity%2C%20aim%20to%20create%20a%20favorable%20environment%20for%20the%20defense%20start-up%20ecosystem.%20The%20move%20aligns%20with%20the%20Innovations%20for%20Defence%20Excellence%20(iDEX)%20and%20Technology%20Development%20Fund%20(TDF)%20schemes%2C%20reflecting%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20'Ease%20of%20Do