t%20a%20meeting%20in%20Nanded%20(Maharashtra)%20in%20March%202014%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20announced%20in%20his%20inimitable%20style%20that%20he%20would%20send%20Ashok%20Chavan%20to%20jail%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20six%20months%E2%80%9D%20should%20he%20become%20the%20prime%20minister.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20battle%20for%20the%20third%20term%2C%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20figured%20in%20the%20Adarsh%20Scam%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98White%20Paper%E2%80%99%20presented%20by%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20early%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Ashok%20Chavan%20recently%20dumped%20the%20Congress%20and%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20But%2C%20as%20per%20the%20policy%20to%20first%20accuse%20an%20opponent%20with%20charges%20of%20corruption%20and%20then%20bring%20him%20into%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98washing%20machine%E2%80%99%E2%80%94that%20has%20become%20a%20hallmark%20of%20the%20Modi-Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20politics%E2%80%94the%20BJP%20has%20nominated%20Chavan%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20president%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20now%20his%20son%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20are%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20most%20valiant%20fighters%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Caccuse%20and%20appropriate%E2%80%9D%20policy.%20The%20nomination%20of%20Manoj%20Jha%20for%20the%20second%20term%20and%20Sanjay%20Yadav%2C%20political%20secretary%20to%20Tejashwi%2C%20is%20a%20clear%20testimony%20to%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20non-compromising%20attitude%20against%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Jha%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20Social%20Work%20at%20Delhi%20University%20who%20was%20among%20over%20145%20MPs%20suspended%20from%20the%20Parliament%20has%20been%20an%20ardent%20advocate%20of%20Social%20Justice%20and%20secularism%20and%20the%20most%20vocal%20critic%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Yadav%20(40)%20an%C2%A0M.SC%20in%20Computer%20Science%20from%20Bhopal%20University%20and%20Management%20graduate%20from%20Indraprastha%20University%20befriended%20Tejashwi%20when%20the%20latter%20was%20a%20player%20at%20the%20IPL%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20Daredevil%20team%20of%20cricket.%20Sanjay%20joined%20Tejashwi%20when%20the%20latter%20began%20working%20for%20his%20party%20in%202011.%20He%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20worked%20diligently%20to%20make%20over%20the%20image%20of%20the%20party%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9Carchetypal%20political%20outfit%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmodern%20one%E2%80%9D%2C%20making%20it%20amenable%20to%20technological%20and%20social%20changes.%20Sanjay%2C%20who%20prefers%20to%20keep%20a%20low%20profile%2C%20away%20from%20the%20media%20glare%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20robust%20presence%20of%20the%20RJD%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20the%20RJD%20looks%20far%20ahead%20and%20more%20forward-looking%20even%20in%20comparison%20to%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%20neighboring%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20By%20nominating%2C%20the%20former%20Bollywood%20actor%2C%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%20wife%20of%20the%20iconic%20thespian%20Amitabh%20Bacchan%20in%20the%20background%20of%20the%20latter%20attending%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20the%20under-construction%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20appears%20incongruous%20with%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cwill%E2%80%9D%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Samajwadi%20party%20leaders%2C%20Pallavi%20Patel%20and%20Swamiprasad%20Maurya%20have%20openly%20opposed%20Jaya%E2%80%99s%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20Ahilesh%20Yadav%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20followed%20the%20politics%20of%20his%20father%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20who%20kept%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20friendship%E2%80%9D%20separate%20from%20his%20political%20consideration.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20had%20nominated%20the%20Hindutva%20leader%2C%20Sakshi%20Maharaj%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20during%20his%20time.%20It%20was%20Mulayam%20who%20brought%20Jaya%20to%20the%20SP%2C%20which%20Akhilesh%20is%20continuing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUncompromising%20Lalu%2C%20Tejashwi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sharp%20contrast%2C%20Lalu%20never%20accommodated%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20friends%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%C2%A0Hindutva%20party%20in%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20space%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20in%20the%20era%20of%20L.%20K%20Advani-A.B%20Vajpayee%20or%20that%20of%20Modi-Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20who%20was%20himself%20a%20harbinger%20of%20generational%20change%20in%20Socialist%20politics%20in%20the%20post-Karpoori%20Thakur%20era%2C%20produced%20and%20promoted%20new%20leadership%20in%20the%20undivided%20Janata%20Dal%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%20Ramkripal%20Yadav%20(a%20Union%20minister%20now)%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Yadav%2C%20former%20MP%20from%20Banka%2C%20Samrat%20Choudhary%20(now%20in%20the%20BJP%20and%20Bihar%20deputy%20CM)%2C%20Bhagwati%20Devi%2C%20a%20woman%20fighter%20of%20the%20era%20of%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20and%20her%20family%20members%20who%20had%20been%20relegated%20to%20political%20periphery%20and%20many%20others%20were%20%E2%80%9Cproducts%E2%80%9D%20of%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20experiment%20with%20the%20youths%20of%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20Tejashwi%20has%20followed%20up%20on%20his%20father%20by%20filling%20his%20party%20with%20several%20young%20but%20talented%20youngsters.%20Recently%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20three%20scholars%20from%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Jayant%20Jigyasu%2C%20Priyanka%20Bharti%20and%20Kanchana%20Yadav%20as%20its%20national%20spokespersons%20who%20are%20diligently%20articulating%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20lines%20and%20philosophy%20in%20the%20media.%20Another%20professor%20at%20Delhi%20University%2C%20Nawal%20Kishore%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20grooming%20the%20youngsters%20in%20the%20educational%20campuses%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJDU-BJP%E2%80%99s%20nominees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20RJD%20encouraging%20new%20leadership%2C%20the%20ruling%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20adopted%20a%20very%20different%20yardstick%20in%20making%20nominations%20to%20the%20Upper%20House.%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20%E2%80%9Crewarded%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20Jha%20who%20was%20said%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98key%20link%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20(Nitish%E2%80%99s)%20switchover%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Jha%20was%20previously%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20working%20as%20a%20private%20secretary%20to%20the%20party%20MP%2C%20Rajiv%20Pratap%20Rudi%20and%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Arun%20Jaitely.%20After%20joining%20the%20JDU%2C%20he%20was%20said%20to%20have%20his%20close%20links%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20brass%20alive.%20He%20was%20said%20to%20have%20played%20the%20%E2%80%98key%20link%E2%80%99%20between%20Nitish%20and%20the%20BJP%20when%20the%20CM%20had%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202017%20also.%20He%20is%2C%20apparently%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20suited%E2%80%9D%20for%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20politics%20of%20%E2%80%9Cflip-flops%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20keeping%20with%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98penchant%E2%80%99%20to%20promote%20their%20own%20brand%20of%20%E2%80%98loyalists%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20left%20out%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%E2%80%94a%20highly%20respected%20and%20most%20articulate%20face%20of%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20from%20the%20Vajpayee-Advani%20era%E2%80%93and%20preferred%20Dharmsheela%20Gupta%20and%20Bhim%20Singh%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20But%20then%20Bhim%20Singh%20too%20learnt%20the%20ropes%20of%20politics%20in%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20school%20of%20%E2%80%98Social%20Justice%E2%80