lso%20said%20no%20complaints%20have%20been%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attempt%20by%20the%20Congress%20has%20implications%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20her%20party%20will%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Congress%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20the%20party%20delegation%20was%20stopped%20twice%2C%20once%20at%20Sarberia%20and%20then%20in%20Rampur%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Rampur%20is%20close%20to%20the%20jetty%20from%20where%20ferries%20are%20available%20to%20go%20to%20the%20island%20of%20Sandeshkhali.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20stopped%20them%2C%20citing%20prohibitory%20orders%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20chief%20minister%20is%20the%20Bengali%20queen%20of%20cruelty.%20The%20people%20of%20Bengal%20and%20all%20of%20India%20have%20seen%20you%20for%20who%20you%20are.%20From%20the%20panchayat%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20MPs%2C%20all%20are%20yours.%20Did%20you%20not%20know%20something%20of%20this%20kind%20was%20happening%20in%20Sandeshkhali%3F%20You%20have%20spoken%20out%20in%20favour%20of%20Shahjahan%20earlier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstituted%20by%20party%20President%20%C2%A0JP%20Nadda%2C%20the%20BJP's%20delegation%20consists%20of%20six%20MPs%2C%20including%20two%20Union%20ministers%2C%20and%20is%20led%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Annapurna%20Devi.%20The%20BJP%20team%20was%20also%20stopped%20in%20Rampur%20and%2C%20after%20starting%20a%20sit-in%20protest%2C%20Annapurna%20Devi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20only%20the%20police%20had%20shown%20the%20same%20urgency%20in%20arresting%20Shahjahan%20as%20they%20have%20in%20stopping%20us...%20If%20the%20police%20had%20acted%20when%20the%20women%20in%20the%20village%20were%20being%20tortured%20by%20Shahjahan's%20goons%20and%20were%20crying%20out%20for%20justice%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20to%20see%20this%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20was%20attacked%20by%20a%20mob%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20house%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20ration%20scam%20on%20January%205.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20women%20named%20alleged%20two%20of%20Shahjahan's%20aides%2C%20Shibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%2C%20have%20been%20harassing%20them.%20While%20Sardar%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20the%20police%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20Hazra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20blamed%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20situation%20and%20said%20there%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BRSS%20base%26quot%3B%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20allowed%20injustice%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20sent%20(representatives%20of)%20the%20state%20women's%20commission%20(to%20Sandeshkhali)%20immediately%20and%2017%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20in%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20they%20(the%20BJP)%20entered%20the%20area%20and%20targeted%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20through%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20then%20they%20started%20the%20trouble%20there%20by%20getting%20people%20in.%20There%20is%20an%20RSS%20base%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20There%20were%20riots%20earlier%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708084260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fb9rql3g8_bjp-delegation-sandeshkhali_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-delegations-stopped-from-going-to-bengals-sandeshkhali-5069820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20firestorm%20over%20the%20alleged%20harassment%20of%20villagers%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%20by%20the%20aides%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20strongman%20escalated%20on%20Friday%20with%20two%20delegations%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20being%20stopped%20from%20going%20to%20the%20island.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-delegations-stopped-from-going-to-bengals-sandeshkhali-5069820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-delegations-stopped-from-going-to-bengals-sandeshkhali-5069820%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-congress-delegations-stopped-from-going-to-bengals-sandeshkhali-5069820%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy.%20Experts%20explain%20why%20moms%20are%20often%20behind%20the%20abuse.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20in%202024%2C%20smiling%20for%20photos%20with%20long%20brown%20hair%20and%20wearing%20a%20black%20lace%20blouse%2C%20and%20silver%20jewelry%2C%20on%20the%20left%3B%20right%2C%20an%20undated%20photo%20from%20the%20Blanchard%20family%20showing%20a%20young%20Gypsy%20Rose%2C%20with%20large%20glasses%20and%20a%20baseball%20cap%20on%2C%20smiling%20while%20her%20mother%20Dee%20Dee%2C%20in%20a%20white%20t-shirt%2C%20pink%20floral%20dress%2C%20and%20silver%20necklace%2C%20smiles%20behind%20her%20while%20embracing%20Gypsy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d87c1ec62ab5daf81fbc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20in%202024%2C%20left%3B%20right%2C%20an%20undated%20photo%20of%20a%20young%20Gypsy%20Rose%20and%20Dee%20Dee%20Blanchard.%3Cp%3EJamie%20McCarthy%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Courtesy%20of%20the%20Blanchard%20family%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMunchausen%20syndrome%20by%20proxy%20is%20a%20form%20of%20child%20abuse%20where%20a%20parent%20or%20carer%20fabricates%20symptoms%20of%20illness%20in%20a%20child.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20also%20known%20as%20fabricated%20or%20induced%20illness%20(FII)%2C%20per%20the%20UK's%20National%20Health%20Service.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20often%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrime%20of%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20usually%20committed%20by%20women%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20did%20think%20it%20was%20me%20and%20my%20mom%20against%20the%20world.%20I%20thought%20she%20was%20my%20best%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordyn%20Hope%2C%20a%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%20advocate%20who%20was%20medically%20abused%20by%20their%20mother%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMunchausen%20syndrome%20by%20proxy%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fmental-health%2Fconditions%2Ffabricated-or-induced-illness%2Foverview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efabricated%20or%20induced%20illness%20(FII)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20form%20of%20child%20abuse%20that%20grabbed%20headlines%20late%20last%20year%20following%20the%20release%20of%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlanchard%20served%20eight%20years%20after%20being%20convicted%20for%20her%20role%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20her%20mother%2C%20Clauddine%20%26quot%3BDee%20Dee%26quot%3B%20Blanchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20wanted%20out%20of%20my%20situation%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20the%20only%20way%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGMA%2Fstatus%2F1743252348409889018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGood%20Morning%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20her%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Blanchard's%20arrest%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20Dee%20Dee%20had%20spent%20much%20of%20Gypsy%20Rose's%20life%20persuading%20her%20and%20others%20that%20her%20daughter%20was%20terminally%20ill%20and%20forcing%20her%20to%20undergo%20many%20unnecessary%20medical%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Blanchard's%20story%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20tale%20of%20deceit%20and%20abuse%2C%20she%20is%20one%20of%20many%20to%20have%20suffered%20from%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20several%20experts%20and%20one%20victim%20about%20who%20typically%20carries%20out%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20attends%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prison%20Confessions%20Of%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%26quot%3B%20Red%20Carpet%20Event%20on%20January%2005%2C%202024%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bcd3086fcb546d2d4b7a2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%20attends%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prison%20Confessions%20Of%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard%26quot%3B%20Red%20Carpet%20Event%20on%20January%2005%2C%202024%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3Cp%3EJamie%20McCarthy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHope%2C%20whose%20pronouns%20are%20they%2Fthem%2C%20said%20their%20mother%20subjected%20them%20to%20numerous%20hospital%20visits%20and%20treatments%20for%20made-up%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20claimed%20I%20had%20rare%20blood%20diseases%2C%20saying%20I%20had%20neutropenia%20which%20is%20a%20rare%20disease%20that%20affects%20white%20blood%20cells%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHope%20now%20knows%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20neutropenia%2C%20but%20they%20were%20made%20to%20believe%20they%20did%20until%20the%20age%20of%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20even%20put%20through%20unnecessary%20major%20back%20surgery%20and%20a%20spinal%20fusion%20at%2015%2C%20leaving%20them%20with%20four%20screws%20and%20two%20rods%20in%20their%20back%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHope's%20story%20is%20reflective%20of%20a%20much%20wider%20pattern%20that%20shows%20that%20women%20are%20often%20behind%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStudies%20suggest%20moms%20are%20often%20the%20perpetrators%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F28750264%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20in%20many%20cases%20of%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%2C%20women%20were%20the%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20which%20looked%20at%20796%20cases%20of%20the%20abuse%2C%20found%20that%2097.6%25%20of%20the%20offenders%20were%20women%20and%2095.6%25%20were%20the%20victim's%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeatrice%20Yorker%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20California%20State%20University%2C%20Los%20Angeles's%20College%20of%20Health%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20this%20was%20likely%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bwomen's%20roles%20in%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20their%20domain.%20This%20is%20where%20women%20have%20the%20utmost%20power%20and%20control%20over%20their%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarc%20Feldman%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%2C%20agreed%2C%20saying%20that%20as%20women%20are%20frequently%20the%20primary%20caregivers%20for%20children%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20simply%20have%20more%20access%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20is%20often%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrime%20of%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobodyshouldbelieveme.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndrea%20Dunlop%2C%20who%20created%20the%20podcast%20Nobody%20Should%20Believe%20Me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20hit%20true%20crime%20show%20about%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Babusers%20will%20look%20for%20places%20where%20they%20have%20power%20because%20abuse%20is%20an%20abuse%20of%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20only%20places%20that%20we%20give%20women%20authority%20is%20over%20children.%20This%20arena%20of%20managing%20a%20child's%20medical%20care%20is%20the%20place%20where%20we%20cede%20full%20authority%20to%20the%20female%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20Dunlop%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFather%20figures%20are%20also%20often%20absent%20in%20cases%20of%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%2C%20Hope%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20case%20for%20Blanchard%2C%20whose%20parents%20separated%20shortly%20before%20she%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERod%20Blanchard%20had%20been%20so%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20his%20daughter's%20true%20health%20that%20the%20first%20time%20he%20saw%20her%20walk%20was%20in%20a%20news%20report%20on%20her%20arraignment%20hearing%20following%20Dee%20Dee's%20murder%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fmichelledean%2Fdee-dee-wanted-her-daughter-to-be-sick-gypsy-wanted-her-mom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuzzFeed%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20so%20confused%20that%20his%20first%20thought%20was%20how%20happy%20he%20was%20that%20she%20was%20walking%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dee%20dee%20and%20gypsy%20rose%20in%20front%20of%20a%20home.%20gypsy%20rose%20is%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wooden%20ramp%20and%20they're%20both%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658de9caec62ab5daf7f6375%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221641%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDee%20Dee%20Blanchard%20and%20Gypsy%20Rose%20Blanchard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Blanchard%20Family%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20Munchausen%20by%20proxy%20occurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20definite%20answer%20as%20to%20why%20this%20form%20of%20abuse%20occurs%2C%20but%20the%20UK's%20National%20Health%20Service%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fmental-health%2Fconditions%2Ffabricated-or-induced-illness%2Foverview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENHS%3C%2Fa%3E)%20says%20it%20may%20be%20influenced%20by%20the%20the%20parent%20or%20carer%20attempting%20to%20gain%20something%2C%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20as%20attention%2C%20support%20or%20closeness%20to%20the%20child.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20adds%20that%20it%20may%20also%20stem%20from%20having%20%26quot%3Banxiety%20or%20incorrect%20beliefs%20about%20their%20child's%20health%2C%20and%20they%20need%20these%20beliefs%20to%20be%20confirmed%20and%20acted%20upon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerpetrators%20are%20usually%20seeking%20%26quot%3Battention%2C%20sympathy%2C%20and%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Feldman%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20could%20become%20exasperated%20in%20women%20after%20giving%20birth%2C%20when%20their%20personalities%20can%20be%20%26quot%3Bsubsumed%20under%20the%20category%20of%20mother%20or%20superwoman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20defined%20by%20their%20children%2C%20not%20by%20their%20own%20achievements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmma%20Milne%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20in%20criminal%20law%20and%20criminal%20justice%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Durham%20whose%20research%20interests%20include%20gender%20and%20crime%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20believed%20fabricated%20illness%20as%20a%20form%20of%20abuse%20was%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20a%20consequence%20of%20a%20psychiatric%20condition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NHS%20notes%20that%20many%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20abuse%20have%20%26quot%3Bborderline%20personality%20disorders%20characterised%20by%20emotional%20instability%2C%20impulsiveness%20and%20disturbed%20thinking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmunchausen-by-proxy-illness-women-gypsy-rose-blanchard-mother-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publish