ar-old%20was%20being%20held%20about%2040%20miles%20north%20of%20Arctic%20Circle.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20was%20an%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20Russian%20president%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlexey%20Navalny%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20fiercest%20political%20nemesis%2C%20has%20died%20suddenly%20at%20the%20age%20of%2047%2C%20Russia's%20prison%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Prison%20Service%20said%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbc.ru%2Fpolitics%2F16%2F02%2F2024%2F65cf45199a794749e34efc8e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-opposition-leader-alexei-navalny-speaks-out-after-mysterious-disappearance-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavalny%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20unwell%20after%20taking%20a%20walk%20while%20in%20prison%20and%20almost%20immediately%20lost%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedics%20were%20called%20and%20tried%20to%20revive%20him%2C%20but%20he%20was%20quickly%20pronounced%20dead%2C%20a%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsaid.It%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20reason%20for%20his%20death%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavalny%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20a%20detention%20facility%20about%2040%20miles%20north%20of%20the%20Arctic%20Circle%2C%20where%20he%20had%20been%20serving%20a%2019-year%20sentence%20that%20was%20widely%20seen%20as%20punishment%20for%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20Russian%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Navalny%20had%20been%20Putin's%20most%20formidable%20domestic%20critic%2C%20criticizing%20what%20he%20characterized%20as%20the%20corruption%20and%20ineptitude%20of%20the%20Russian%20president%20and%20his%20inner%20circle.%20He%20organized%20large%20anti-Kremlin%20protests%20that%20were%20suppressed%20by%20Russian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira%20Yarmysh%2C%20Navalny's%20spokesperson%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKira_Yarmysh%2Fstatus%2F1758457690429305206%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20Navalny's%20death%20was%20not%20confirmed.%20%26quot%3BAlexey's%20lawyer%20is%20currently%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Kharp.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20have%20some%20information%2C%20we%20will%20report%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20Leonid%20Volkov%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fleonidvolkov%2Fstatus%2F1758456557770101005%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BRussian%20authorities%20publish%20a%20confession%20that%20they%20killed%20Alexey%20Navalny%20in%20prison.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20any%20way%20to%20confirm%20it%20or%20to%20prove%20this%20isn't%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20leaders%20have%20praised%20Navalny%2C%20with%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20saying%20that%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fiercest%20advocate%20for%20Russian%20democracy%2C%20Alexei%20Navalny%20demonstrated%20incredible%20courage%20throughout%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20said%20that%20it%20held%20Russia%20responsible%20for%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlexei%20Navalny%20fought%20for%20the%20values%20of%20freedom%20and%20democracy.%20For%20his%20ideals%2C%20he%20made%20the%20ultimate%20sacrifice%2C%26quot%3B%20European%20Council%20President%20Charles%20Michel%20posted%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThe%20EU%20holds%20the%20Russian%20regime%20for%20sole%20responsible%20for%20this%20tragic%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20previously%20said%20that%20Russia%20would%20suffer%20%26quot%3Bdevastating%26quot%3B%20consequences%20if%20Navalny%20were%20to%20die%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeduza.io%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fkremlin-spokesman-dmitry-peskov-comments-on-navalny-s-death%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Peskov%20told%20Russian%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Putin%20had%20been%20informed%20of%20Navalny's%20death%20and%20that%20he%20had%20no%20further%20information%20on%20its%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20sudden%20death%20brings%20with%20it%20an%20end%20to%20any%20powerful%20political%20opposition%20to%20Putin%20that%20still%20existed%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20Navalny%20became%20ill%20on%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Moscow%20from%20Tomsk%2C%20Siberia.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Germany%2C%20where%20medical%20experts%20said%20he%20was%20poisoned%20with%20a%20chemical%20nerve%20agent%20from%20the%20Novichok%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Russia%20denied%20that%20Putin%20was%20behind%20the%20poisoning%20and%20refused%20to%20open%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20the%20European%20Court%20of%20Human%20Rights%20ruled%20violated%20Navalny's%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavalny%20recovered%20in%20Germany%20for%20five%20months%2C%20before%20returning%20to%20Russia%2C%20where%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20breaking%20news%20story.%20More%20to%20follow.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexey-navalny-putin-main-political-foe-died-prison-russian-officials-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708083427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf478df533b039a8846428%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falexey-navalny-putin-main-political-foe-died-prison-russian-officials-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alexey%20Navalny%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20unwell%20after%20a%20walk%20and%20almost%20immediately%20lost%20consciousness%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Russian%20prison%20service.%22%2C%22autho