the%20portrayal%20of%20matrimony%20in%20the%20drama.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fhyun-bin-and-son-ye-jins-wedding-inspires-scene-in-upcoming-k-drama-queen-of-tears%2Farticleshow%2F107754706.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Madame%20Web%20Is%20Dead-On-Arrival%20Fare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20insufferably%20clunky%2C%20over-expository%20and%20rudderless%20origin%20story%20of%20a%20fringe%20character%20from%20the%20Marvel%20multiverse%2C%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%20spins%20a%20yarn%20so%20insubstantial%20that%20it%20snaps%20in%20no%20time%20and%20is%20all%20over%20the%20place.%20Not%20a%20pretty%20sight%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%2010%20to%2020%20minutes%20in%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20see%20the%20bleak%20future%20of%20the%20two-hour%20movie%20-%20and%20the%20franchise%20that%20might%20be%20on%20the%20anvil%20over%20at%20Sony.%20It%20goes%20nowhere.%20The%20dialogue%20is%20ham-fisted%2C%20the%20action%20amateurish%2C%20the%20visual%20effects%20rudimentary%20and%20the%20final%20outcome%20disastrous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarvel%20fatigue%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20sheer%20ineptitude%20is%20quite%20another.%20The%20two%20mingle%20in%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20directed%20and%20co-written%20(with%20three%20other%20writers)%20by%20S.J.%20Clarkson.%20Their%20toil%20yields%20an%20utterly%20unwarranted%20movie%20that%20should%20have%20been%20better%20off%20nixed%20at%20the%20drafting%20stage.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20acting%2C%20the%20less%20said%20the%20better.%20And%20that%20certainly%20isn't%20for%20want%20of%20effort.%20The%20actors%20strive%20very%20hard%20indeed.%20The%20strain%20shows.%20With%20an%20overload%20of%20inanities%20to%20deal%20with%20and%20tide%20over%2C%20the%20cast%20-%20besides%20Dakota%20Johnson%2C%20it%20includes%20Sydney%20Sweeney%20and%20Tahar%20Rahim%20-%20is%20hard-pressed%20to%20pull%20the%20proceedings%20out%20of%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20little%20humour%20going%20around.%20Most%20of%20the%20film's%20attempts%20at%20being%20funny%20fall%20flat%20and%20the%20bursts%20of%20energy%20that%20peppers%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20too%20overly%20affected%20to%20be%20effective.%20Dakota%20Johnson%2C%20she%20of%20the%20three%2050%20Shades%20films%2C%20is%20saddled%20with%20a%20role%20that%20approximates%20the%20character's%20arc%20in%20the%20film%20-%20until%20the%20very%20end%2C%20she%20struggles%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20and%2For%20what%20she%20can%20be%20if%20she%20were%20to%20put%20her%20mind%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20original%20comic-book%20avatar%2C%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20aged%2C%20sightless%20wheelchair%20user%20endowed%20with%20powers%20that%20help%20her%20see%20the%20future%20in%20time%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stop%20or%20alter%20unwanted%20events.%20In%20the%20movie%2C%20Cassandra%20%26quot%3BCassie%26quot%3B%20Webb%20(Johnson)%20is%20a%20New%20York%20Fire%20Department%20ambulance%20driver%20who%20is%20constantly%20racing%20against%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fs_76M4c4LTo%3Fsi%3DdFcwMrtIi0XjVqwW%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20accident%20triggers%20a%20startling%20change%20in%20her.%20She%20experiences%20disturbing%20visions%20of%20the%20immediate%20future%20that%20alarm%20and%20forewarn%20her.%20Unlike%20the%20Cassandra%20of%20Greek%20mythology%2C%20three%20girls%20she%20decides%20to%20help%20against%20a%20malefic%20force%20believe%20her%20helpful%20prognoses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20up%2C%20Cassie%20saves%20(very%20casually%2C%20if%20not%20unintentionally)%20a%20pigeon%20from%20a%20death%20foretold%20and%20then%20moves%20on%20to%20bigger%20creatures%20and%20lives%20as%20it%20dawns%20upon%20her%2C%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20help%20from%20a%20figure%20hidden%20in%20her%20past%2C%20that%20she%20is%20no%20ordinary%2030-year-old%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villain%2C%20played%20by%20Rahim%20(the%20French%20actor%20has%20never%20been%20so%20shoddily%20treated%20by%20a%20movie%20script)%2C%20can%20crawl%20on%20ceilings%2C%20swoop%20upon%20his%20prey%20at%20will%20and%20emit%20a%20fatal%20neurotoxin%20from%20his%20hand%2C%20but%20neither%20he%20nor%20the%20film%20has%20a%20way%20of%20wriggling%20out%20of%20the%20web%20of%20mediocrity%20that%20they%20are%20caught%20in.%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20dead-on-arrival%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney's%20Marvel%20movies%2C%20when%20things%20tend%20to%20go%20right%2C%20often%20deliver%20levels%20of%20entertainment%20that%20can%20keep%20audiences%20invested%20in%20the%20make-believe%20world%20that%20they%20conjure%20up%20with%20all%20their%20might.%20In%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nothing%20works.%20Nothing%20at%20all.%20An%20overwhelming%20dullness%20creeps%20into%20everything%20that%20Sony's%20Columbia%20Pictures-produced%20film%20rustles%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20action%20In%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0takes%20place%20in%20New%20York%20in%202003.%20The%20period%20movie%20feel%20that%20Director%20S.J.%20Clarkson%20and%20her%20production%20designers%20seek%20to%20impart%20to%20it%20-%20to%20help%20the%20audience%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20time%20and%20place%2C%20Pepsi%20cans%20of%20a%20certain%20vintage%2C%20a%20giant%20Calvin%20Klein%20hoarding%20through%20which%20the%20heroine%20drives%20an%20ambulance%20and%20a%20poster%20announcing%20Beyonce's%20debut%20album%20are%20thrown%20in%20-%20seeps%20into%20the%20overall%20look%20and%20texture%20of%20the%20film%20and%20not%20always%20in%20a%20good%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20stylistically%20obsolete%20and%20technically%20sloppy%20-%20it%20is%20at%20most%20times%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20time%20when%20Hollywood%20superhero%20movies%20were%20only%20beginning%20to%20find%20their%20way%20forward%20and%20paving%20the%20ground%20for%20a%20spate%20the%20MCU%20fare%20that%20now%20crowds%20everything%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0opens%20in%20the%20Peruvian%20Amazon%20where%20Cassie's%20pregnant%20mother%2C%20Constance%20(Kerry%20Bishe)%2C%20is%20on%20an%20expedition%20to%20look%20for%20a%20rare%20spider%20with%20healing%20abilities.%20She%20is%20betrayed%20by%20an%20evil%20associate%2C%20Ezekiel%20Sims%20(Rahim)%2C%20who%20wants%20the%20spider%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstance%20dies%20but%20not%20before%20being%20bitten%20by%20ab%20arachnid%20and%20giving%20birth%20to%20Cassandra%20%26quot%3BCassie%26quot%3B%20Webb%2C%20who%20acquires%20psychic%20powers%20thanks%20to%20the%20beneficial%20venom%20that%20passed%20on%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20film%20has%20neither%20bite%20nor%20bang%20as%20the%20baddie%2C%20who%2C%20too%2C%20foresees%20his%20death%20in%20a%20vision%20and%20sets%20out%20to%20eliminate%20the%20three%20teenage%20girls%20who%20he%20knows%20will%20cause%20his%20demise.%20The%20girls%20are%20just%2C%20girls%20but%20each%20possesses%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20Spider-Woman.%20Still%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20they%20are%20well%20away%20form%20acquiring%20any%20real%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20where%20Cassie%20comes%20in.%20She%20has%20visions%20that%20reveal%20troubling%20events%20of%20the%20immediate%20future.%20She%20babysits%20the%20three%20girls%20-%20Julia%20Cornwall%20(Sweeney)%2C%20Mattie%20Franklin%20(Celeste%20O'Connor)%20and%20Anya%20Corazon%20(Isabela%20Merced)%20-%20babes%20in%20the%20woods%20who%20need%20all%20the%20handholding%20that%20they%20can%20get%20from%20Cassie%20-%20through%20the%20tough%20situations%20thrown%20at%20them%20by%20the%20crawling%20menace%20that%20Ezekiel%20turns%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20one%20were%20able%20to%20say%20that%20all%20this%20is%20fun%20while%20it%20lasts%2C%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%20might%20have%20just%20about%20passed%20muster.%20Since%20it%20isn't%2C%20the%20movie%20is%20exhausting%2C%20pointless%20and%20totally%20bereft%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20flashy%20-%20and%20superficial%20-%20craft%20that%20superhero%20movies%20usually%20ride%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20all%20very%20well%20to%20rustle%20up%20a%20female-centric%20superhero%20movie%20but%20all%20that%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20likely%20to%20do%20is%20give%20all%20that%20are%20involved%20with%20the%20making%20of%20this%20forgettable%20movie%20a%20bad%20name%20that%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20live%20down.%20It%20would%20be%20regarded%20as%20the%20worst%20of%20its%20kind%20had%20it%20not%20been%20competing%20with%20Morbius%2C%20the%20Sony%20Spider-Man%20Universe%20monstrosity%20that%20preceded%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20very%20low%20bar%20to%20aim%20for%2C%20%3Cem%3EMadame%20Web%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ebarely%20makes%20it.%20Heed%20the%20future%20-%20it%20has%20waste%20of%20time%20written%20all%20over%20-%20and%20change%20it.%20Give%20this%20movie%20a%20miss.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708081740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fp2hrv82o_madame_625x300_16_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmadame-web-review-rudderless-origin-story-is-dead-on-arrival-fare-1-star-5069505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madame%20Web%20Review%3A%20With%20an%20overload%20of%20inanities%20to%20deal%20with%20and%20tide%20over%2C%20the%20cast%20-%20besides%20Dakota%20Johnson%2C%