Baba%20Vanga%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20made%20several%20predictions%20during%20her%20lifetime%20that%20many%20say%20became%20true.%20Also%20called%20the%20Nostradamus%20of%20the%20Balkans%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Frise-in-terror-attacks-to-terrifying-weather-events-baba-vangas-predictions-for-2024-4546962%5C%22%3E%20Baba%20Vanga%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20said%20to%20have%20foretold%20major%20world%20events%20like%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attacks%2C%20the%20death%20of%20Princess%20Diana%2C%20the%20Chernobyl%20disaster%2C%20and%20Brexit.%20For%202024%2C%20she%20reportedly%20made%20several%20prophecies%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20have%20come%20true.%20These%20are%20the%20economic%20crisis%20plaguing%20countries%20like%20Japan%20and%20the%20UK%20and%20development%20of%20a%20cancer%20vaccine%20by%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20these%20major%20developments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussia's%20Cancer%20Vaccine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Vladimir%20Putin%20recently%20said%20that%20Russian%20scientists%20are%20close%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-very-close-to-creating-cancer-vaccines-says-vladimir-putin-5058785%5C%22%3Ecreating%20a%20vaccine%20for%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20could%20soon%20be%20available%20to%20patients.%20Mr%20Putin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20very%20close%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20so-called%20cancer%20vaccines%20and%20immunomodulatory%20drugs%20of%20a%20new%20generation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20soon%20they%20will%20be%20effectively%20used%20as%20methods%20of%20individual%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20Moscow%20forum%20on%20future%20technologies.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20not%20specify%20the%20types%20of%20cancer%20the%20proposed%20vaccines%20would%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Crisis%20in%20Japan%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaba%20Vanga%20also%20reportedly%20foretold%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20economic%20crisis%20that%20will%20impact%20the%20global%20economy%20in%202024.%20Factors%20like%20rising%20debt%20levels%20and%20escalating%20geopolitical%20tensions%20will%20be%20the%20reasons%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20UK%20sank%20into%20recession%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20due%20to%20high%20inflation%20and%20a%20cost-of-living%20crisis%2C%20dealing%20a%20blow%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20before%20this%20year's%20election.%20According%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20gross%20domestic%20product%20shrank%200.3%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%20after%20contracting%200.1%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20prior%20three%20months.%20That%20places%20the%20economy%20in%20recession%2C%20which%20is%20defined%20as%20two%20successive%20quarters%20of%20falling%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20economy%20also%20shrank%20for%20two%20quarters%20in%20a%20row.%20The%20country's%20GDP%20shrank%20by%200.4%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20last%20three%20months%20of%202023%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20year%20earlier.%20It%20also%20slipped%20below%20Germany%20last%20year%20to%20fourth%20place%20in%20the%20list%20of%20world's%20biggest%20economies.%20Despite%20growing%201.9%20per%20cent%2C%20Japan's%20nominal%202023%20gross%20domestic%20product%20in%20dollar%20terms%20was%20%244.2%20trillion%2C%20government%20data%20showed%2C%20compared%20with%20%244.5%20trillion%20for%20Germany%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20released%20there%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20of%20the%20other%20predictions%20of%20the%20Bulgarian%20mystic%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20warned%20of%20increased%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Europe%20and%20suggested%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20country%26quot%3B%20will%20conduct%20biological%20weapons%20tests%20or%20attacks%20ne