for%20opportunities%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteaching-in-thailand-tips-salary-not-easy-gig-relocation-essay-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteach%20English%20in%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Europe.%20I%20applied%20to%20many%20places%20before%20getting%20an%20offer%20at%20a%20school%20in%20Wakayama%2C%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20visited%20Japan%20the%20year%20before%20on%20vacation%2C%20and%20when%20I%20got%20the%20offer%20letter%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20wait%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-moved-to-japan-and-am-saving-more-than-1800-a-month-on-rent-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20move%20there%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20excited%20about%20my%20fresh%20start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20came%20with%20a%20monthly%20salary%20of%20250%2C000%20yen%2C%20or%20around%20%241%2C700%2C%20and%20a%20company%20car.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20the%20pay%20cut%20because%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20was%20lower.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20a%20few%20years%20teaching%20before%20becoming%20a%20franchise%20owner%20of%20a%20school%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-moving-to-japan-westerner-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaches%20English%20to%20Japanese%20students%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20my%20wife%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Osaka.%20We%20got%20married%20and%20had%20a%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20move%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20Japan%20and%20America%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20military.%20I%20got%20a%20job%20as%20an%20IT%20specialist%20in%20Georgia%2C%20and%20my%20family%20and%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20the%20US.%20My%20wife%20was%20wary%20at%20first%20about%20leaving%20Japan%2C%20but%20the%20job%20paid%20better%20than%20teaching%2C%20so%20she%20got%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3