-allegations-of-election-rigging%2Farticleshow%2F107750949.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fbalochistan-protests-persist-amid-allegations-of-election-rigging%2Famp_articleshow%2F107750949.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fbalochistan-protests-persist-amid-allegations-of-election-rigging%2Famp_articleshow%2F107750949.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20Narayan%20Row%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20Hit%20My%20Hand...%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Student%20Whose%20Phone%20Thrown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20viral%20video%20incident%2C%20in%20which%20singer%20Aditya%20Narayan%20was%20seen%20throwing%20a%20fan's%20phone%20away%20during%20his%20concert%20in%20Bhilai%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20took%20a%20new%20turn%C2%A0after%20the%20student%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20denied%C2%A0the%20allegation%20of%20%26quot%3Bdragging%20the%20singer's%20feet%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zoomtventertainment.com%2Fcelebrity%2Faditya-narayans-concert-row-student-involved-says-singer-obliged-to-take-phones-for-selfies-says-no-one-hit-him-excl-article-107738169%5C%22%3EZoom%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0The%20student%2C%20identified%20as%20Lovkesh%20Chandravanshi%2C%20is%20in%20third-year%20BSc%20at%20Rungta%20College.%C2%A0Narrating%20the%20whole%20incident%20in%20detail%2C%20he%20told%20Zoom%2C%20%26quot%3BWhatever%20happened%20was%20so%20sudden.%20I%20had%20not%20expected%20this%20to%20happen%20to%20me.%20Alag%20sa%20feel%20ho%20raha%20hai%20(I%20feel%20very%20different).%20The%20concert%20was%20going%20on%20and%20I%20was%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20stage.%20Aditya%20sir%20was%20performing%20and%20he%20was%20also%20taking%20everyone's%20phones%20and%20clicking%20selfies%20for%20them.%20I%20was%20right%20by%20the%20stage%20so%20I%20also%20gave%20my%20phone%20to%20him%20for%20the%20selfie%20but%20he%20hit%20my%20hand%20with%20his%20mic%20and%20then%20threw%20my%20phone%20away%20for%20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20brother%20was%20standing%20next%20to%20me%20too.%20Aditya%20is%20a%20huge%20star%20and%20we%20love%20him%20that%20is%20why%20we%20went.%20He%20was%20taking%20selfies%20with%20everyone%20so%20I%20thought%20he%20would%20take%20with%20me%20too%20that's%20why%20I%20gave%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Aditya%20Narayan%2C%20the%20student%20also%20mentioned%20during%20the%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20should%20have%20not%20done%20what%20he%20did%20to%20me%20even%20if%20it%20was%20some%20other%20student.%20We%20are%20all%20his%20fans%20and%20we%20love%20him%20a%20lot%20that%20is%20why%20we%20go%20to%20his%20concert.%20Hamare%20yaha%20kalakaro%20ki%20kami%20nahi%20hai%20vaise%20(We%20don't%20have%20dearth%20of%20artistes%20in%20our%20country).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsinger-aditya-narayans-reaction-after-bhilai-concert-video-goes-viral-i-am-answerable-to-the-almighty-5058834%5C%22%3EThe%20student's%20version%20lies%20in%20a%20sharp%20contradiction%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20what%20the%20concert's%20event%20manager%20earlier%20told%20Zoom.%20After%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20and%20Aditya%20was%20slammed%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Internet%2C%20the%20event%20manager%20issued%20a%20statement.%20He%20told%20Zoom%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20boy%20was%20not%20even%20a%20college%20student%2C%20he%20must%20be%20someone%20from%20outside%20the%20college.%20He%20was%20constantly%20dragging%20Aditya's%20feet%20nonstop.%20He%20was%20very%20irritating.%20He%20banged%20his%20phone%20on%20Aditya's%20feet%20multiple%20times.%20After%20that%20only%20did%20he%20lose%20his%20cool.%20He%20must%20have%20taken%20almost%20200%20selfies%20with%20this%20student.%20The%20whole%20concert%20went%20smooth%20apart%20from%20this.%20After%20this%20incident%2C%20the%20show%20went%20on%20for%20almost%20two%20hours.%20If%20the%20student%20was%20right%2C%20he%20would%20have%20come%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20manager%20added%20during%20his%20interaction%20with%20Zoom%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20Darshan%20Rawal%20stopped%20doing%20such%20college%20events%20because%20these%20kinds%20of%20activities%20keep%20happening%20in%20every%20city.%20People%20don't%20know%20the%20truth%20behind%20everything.%20You%20just%20see%20one%20side.%20He%20kept%20continuously%20hitting%20and%20dragging%20Aditya%2C%20what%20if%20he%20had%20fallen%20down%3F%20If%20this%20boy%20was%20right%2C%20he%20would%20have%20come%20forward%20and%20told%20the%20college%20authorities%20that%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20him.%20I%20have%20been%20connected%20with%20the%20college%20since%20many%20years%20and%20they%20haven't%20had%20a%20good%20concert%20like%20this%20one%20ever.%20They%20have%20said%20so%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20Aditya%20Narayan%20also%20reacted%20to%20the%20incident.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20Aditya%20Narayan%20told%20Times%20Now%2C%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20no%20comments.%20I%20am%20answerable%20to%20the%20Almighty.%20That's%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICYMI%2C%20This%20is%20the%20video%20we%20are%20talking%20about%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAditya%20Narayan%2C%20son%20of%20ace%20singer%20Udit%20Narayan%2C%20gained%20popularity%20through%20fans'%20support%2C%20but%20now%20he%20assaults%20a%20fan%20by%20throwing%20his%20mobile.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAdityaNarayan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AdityaNarayan%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20be%20banned%20from%20participating%20in%20concerts%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20apologize%20to%20the%20fan%20for%20his%20actions.%20He%20needs%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fn2Chkx5FIr%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fn2Chkx5FIr%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Deepak%20Khatri%20(%40Deepakkhatri812)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeepakkhatri812%2Fstatus%2F1757111120408478183%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Narayan%20has%20many%20hit%20songs%20to%20his%20credit%20including%20Ishqyaun%20Dhishqyaun%2C%20Main%20Nikla%20Gaddi%20Leke%2C%20and%20Tattad%20Tattad%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708075260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpdaqo8h_aditya-_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Faditya-narayan-row-student-whose-phone-was-thrown-says-he-hit-my-hand-with-his-mic-5068925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20Aditya%20Narayan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20answerable%20to%20the%20Almighty%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Faditya-narayan-row-student-whose-phone-was-thrown-says-he-hit-my-hand-with-his-mic-5068925%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Faditya-narayan-row-student-whose-phone-was-thrown-says-he-hit-my-hand-with-his-mic-5068925%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Faditya-narayan-row-student-whose-phone-was-thrown-says-he-hit-my-hand-with-his-mic-5068925%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pacific%20Plate%20Being%20Torn%20Apart%20From%20Japan%20To%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Finds%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEarth's%20rigid%20outer%20shell%20is%20divided%20into%20a%20dozen%20large%20tectonic%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20major%20one%20-%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20-%20is%20being%20pulled%20apart.%20The%20discovery%20has%20been%20made%20by%20researchers%20from%20University%20of%20Toronto%20and%20is%20shedding%20new%20light%20on%20the%20century-old%20model%20of%20plate%20tectonics.%20The%20team%20found%20that%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20scored%20by%20large%20undersea%20faults%20that%20are%20pulling%20it%20apart.%20The%20research%20has%20been%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1029%2F2023GL105452%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGeophysical%20Research%20Letters%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20talks%20about%20the%20enormous%20forces%20that%20are%20tugging%20away%20the%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20undersea%20faults%20are%20hundreds%20of%20kilometres%20long%20and%20thousands%20of%20metres%20deep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20that%20geological%20deformations%20like%20faults%20happen%20on%20the%20continental%20plate%20interiors%20far%20from%20plate%20boundaries.%20But%20we%20didn't%20know%20the%20same%20thing%20was%20happening%20to%20ocean%20plates%2C%26quot%3B%20Erkan%20Gun%2C%20a%20post-doctoral%20researcher%20in%20the%20department%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20in%20the%20Faculty%20of%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Sciences%2C%20told%20phys.org.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we're%20doing%20is%20refining%20plate%20tectonics-the%20theory%20that%20describes%20how%20our%20planet%20works-and%20showing%20those%20plates%20really%20aren't%20as%20pristine%20as%20we%20previously%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Russell%20Pysklywec%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20department%20of%20Earth%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pacific%20plate%2C%20the%20largest%20tectonic%20plate%2C%20constitutes%20most%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20floor%2C%20stretching%20along%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20North%20America%20up%20to%20Alaska.%20At%20the%20western%20edge%2C%20it%20runs%20from%20Japan%20to%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plate%20forms%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Ring%20of%20Fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20research%20has%20identified%20new%20points%20at%20which%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20being%20pulled%20down%20into%20the%20mantle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20thought%20that%20because%20the%20sub-oceanic%20plateaus%20are%20thicker%2C%20they%20should%20be%20stronger.%20But%20our%20models%20and%20seismic%20data%20show%20it's%20actually%20the%20opposite%3A%20the%20plateaus%20are%20weaker%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20studied%20four%20plateaus%20in%20the%20western%20Pacific%20Ocean%20-%20the%20Ontong%20Java%2C%20Shatsky%2C%20Hess%20and%20Manihiki%20-%20in%20a%20vast%20area%20roughly%20bounded%20by%20Hawaii%2C%20Japan%2C%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia.%20The%20data%20was%20then%20fed%20to%20a%20supercomputer%2C%20which%20compared%20it%20with%20information%20collected%20in%20studies%20done%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20new%20finding%20like%20this%20overturns%20what%20we've%20understood%20and%20taught%20about%20the%20active%20Earth.%20And%20it%20shows%20that%20there%20are%20still%20radical%20mysteries%20about%20even%20the%20grand%20operation%20of%20our%20evolving%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pysklywec.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708075080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Frdbmaur_tectonic-plate-unsplash_625x300_16_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20research%20has%20identified%20new%20points%20at%20which%20the%20Pacific%20plate%20is%20being%20pulled%20down%20into%20the%20mantle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fpacific-plate-being-torn-apart-from-japan-to-new-zealand-finds-study-5068889%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Fresh%20Bout%20of%20Public%20Unrest%2C%20Arrests%20and%20Arson%3B%20Internet%20Suspended%20in%20Churachandpur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16145341%2FGGBKaMkWoAEYCW5.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Arson%2C%20arrests%20and%20public%20unrest%20continue%20to%20haunt%20Manipur%20as%20internet%20services%20have%20once%20again%20been%20snapped%20by%20the%20state%20government%20in%20the%20Kuki-majority%20Churachandpur%20after%20a%20mob%20attacked%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20office%20in%20the%20border%20town%20on%20February%2015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20Police%2C%20taking%20to%20X%2C%20has%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMob%20numbering%20approximately%20300%E2%80%93400%20(people)%20attempted%20to%20storm%20the%20office%20of%20SP%20CCP%20today%2C%20pelting%20stones%2C%20etc.%20The%20security%20forces%20including%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20is%20responding%20appropriately%20by%20firing%20tear%20gas%20shells%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%20Things%20are%20under%20watch.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20Imphal-based%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTheFrontierManipur%3Fref%3Dembed_page%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Frontier%20Manipur%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20four%20photographs%20on%20February%2016%20morning%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CChurachandpur%20DC%20(deputy%20commissioner)%20office%20was%20burnt%20down%20by%20Kuki%20militants%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20confirm%20this%20news%20independently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmob-storms-sp-office-in-manipurs-churachandpur-after-head-constable-from-kuki-zo-community-was-suspended%2Farticle67850970.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%2C%20one%20person%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20security%20forces%20and%20several%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20SP%20office%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20public%20anger%20was%20due%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20head%20constable%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%20Siamlalpaul%20was%20posted%20at%20the%20Churachandpur%20police%20station.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-mob-fury-in-churachandpur-after-cop-suspension%5C%22%3EImphal-based%20news%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20action%20against%20him%20was%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D%20after%20a%20viral%20video%20clip%20featuring%20him%20was%20circulated.%20It%20allegedly%20showed%20him%20making%20a%20video%20with%20%E2%80%9Carmed%20miscreants%20sitting%20together%20with%20village%20volunteers%E2%80%9D%20from%20his%20Kuki-Zo%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20order%20issued%20by%20Churachandpur%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Shivanand%20Surve%20noted%20that%20Siamlalpaul%20was%20found%20culpable%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgrave%20misconduct%E2%80%9D%20in%20spite%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmember%20of%20a%20disciplined%20force%E2%80%9D%20under%20Rule%2066%2C%20Part%203%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Manual.%20The%20order%20said%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20could%20be%20initiated%20against%20him%20and%20that%20he%20could%20not%20leave%20the%20station%20without%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20SP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20order%20is%20said%20to%20have%20led%20the%20mob%20to%20storm%20the%20SP%20and%20DC%20offices%20in%20Churachandpur.%20The%20mob%20ended%20up%20vandalising%20the%20public%20offices.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESix%20held%20for%20arms%20loot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20state%20police%20has%20arrested%20six%20persons%20in%20the%20arms%20looting%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20on%20February%2013%20at%20the%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion%20(IRBn)%20camp%20in%20Chingarel%20area%20of%20Imphal%20East%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20Police%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20X%20on%20February%2014%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20of%20arms%20looting%20case%20of%205th%20IRBn%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%20by%20an%20unruly%20mob%20on%20the%20night%20of%2013.02.2024%2C%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20arrested%20six%20persons%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%2014)%20and%20they%20have%20been%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20by%20a%20judicial%20magistrate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFour%20Insas%20rifles%2C%20one%20AK%20Ghatak%2C%20two%20magazines%20of%20SLR%2C%20and%2016%20small%20boxes%20of%209mm%20ammunition%20looted%20from%20the%20IRBn%20camp%20have%20also%20been%20recovered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2024%2F02%2F16%2Fmanipur-6-arrested-for-looting-arms-from-irbn-camp%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20police%20did%20not%20mention%20from%20where%20the%20arms%20were%20recovered%2C%20or%20from%20where%20the%20persons%20were%20arrested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20after%20the%20IRBn%20mob%20attack%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20l%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Earge%20number%E2%80%9D%20of%20village%20volunteers%20also%20attempted%20to%20barge%20into%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20Training%20College%20at%20Pangei%20in%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20located%20around%205%20kms%20from%20Chingarel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20X%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20February%2013%2C%20in%20order%20to%20repel%20violent%20mobs%2C%20including%20armed%20miscreants%2C%20trying%20to%20storm%20MPTC%2C%20Pangei%2C%20security%20forces%20resorted%20to%20the%20use%20of%20legal%20force.%20During%20the%20incident%2C%20one%20person%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%20and%20three%20persons%20sustained%20injuries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20suspended%20seven%20IRBn%20personnel%20over%20the%20looting%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20from%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Commandant%20of%205th%20IRB%2C%20Chingarel%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20H.%20Balram%20Singh%20in%20an%20order%20said%20the%20seven%20personnel%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Csuspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20until%20further%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-mob-fury-in-churachandpur-after-cop-suspension%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20this%20move%20too%20was%20taken%20under%20Rule%2066%20of%20the%20Assam%20Police%20Manual%20Part-3%2C%20and%20that%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20may%20be%20initiated%20against%20them%20too%20for%20negligence%20and%20dereliction%20of%20duty.%20All%20suspended%20personnel%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20camp%20without%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20station%20commandant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708074920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16145341%2FGGBKaMkWoAEYCW5.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Attacks%20have%20seen%20large%20mobs%20barge%20into%20police%20stations%20or%20armouries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-churachandpur-arrests-arson-unrest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riot%20Convict%20Extradited%20From%20UAE%20Within%204%20Months%20Of%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20most%20wanted%20criminal%20was%20extradited%20from%20the%20UAE%20on%20Friday%20after%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bgeo-located%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gulf%20by%20Interpol%20channels.%20Narender%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20wanted%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20for%20murder%20and%20rioting%2C%20also%20faced%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20convicted%20in%202009%20and%20jailed%20for%20life.%20Interpol%20had%20issued%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20against%20him%20on%20November%207%20last%20year%20following%20a%20request%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20notice%20was%20then%20circulated%20to%20all%20Interpol%20member%20countries%20to%20identify%20his%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20geo-located%20in%20the%20UAE%20through%20a%20close%20follow-up%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20via%20Interpol%2C%20the%20central%20agency%20said.%20Geo-locating%20someone%20means%20identifying%20the%20geographic%20location%20of%20an%20individual%20based%20on%20data%20collection%20mechanisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20Global%20Operations%20Centre%20coordinated%20with%20its%20National%20Central%20Bureau%20for%20Interpol%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20and%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20to%20secure%20his%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26qu