that%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20our%20exporters.%20We%20will%20continue%20our%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20growth%20is%20recorded%20in%20the%20coming%20period%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20several%20export%20sectors%20recorded%20positive%20growth%20in%20January%2C%20while%20imports%20saw%20declines%20in%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20top%2030%20export%20sectors%2C%2018%20registered%20positive%20growth%20in%20January%20led%20by%20iron%20ore%20(109.8%25)%2C%20tobacco%20(47.3%25)%2C%20meat%2C%20dairy%20and%20poultry%20products%20(26.1%25)%20and%20spices%20(20.5%25).%20On%20the%20imports%20front%2C%2017%20sectors%20clocked%20a%20decline%20in%20shipment%20values%2C%20including%20fertilisers%20(-69.1%25)%2C%20project%20goods%20(-43.9%25)%2C%20and%20raw%20cotton%20(-32.3%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708073815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19151431%2Fimage-920.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-trade-deficit-narrows-to-nine-month-low-in-january-amid-export-growth%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20January%202023%20trade%20deficit%20stood%20at%20%2417.03%20billion%20and%20%2419.8%20billion%20in%20December.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-trade-deficit-narrows-to-nine-month-low-in-january-amid-export-growth%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Corporate%20finance%20firm%20REC%20to%20issue%20multiple-tenor%20bonds%2C%20say%20bankers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708072747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F16%2Ffull%2F1705399428-1809.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcorporate-finance-firm-rec-to-issue-multiple-tenor-bonds-say-bankers