on-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Love%20Storiyaan%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELove%20On%20Air%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Northeast%20has%20always%20been%20a%20tricky%20place%20for%20Hindi%20films%2C%20and%20the%20cultural%20awkwardness%20continues%20in%20Vivek%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELove%20On%20Air%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20following%20two%20rival%20radio%20jockeys%20falling%20in%20love%20in%20Meghalaya.%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20debut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMeenakshi%20Sundareshwar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20infamous%20for%20Hindi-fying%20Madurai%2C%20and%20here%20you%20see%20him%20trying%20to%20be%20more%20cognisant%20of%20that%20fact%20with%20Nicholas%20and%20Rajani%E2%80%99s%20love%20story.%20However%2C%20the%20gaze%20continues%20to%20be%20an%20outsider%E2%80%99s%2C%20with%20hints%20of%20exoticisation%20most%20visible%20in%20a%20voice-over%20straight%20out%20of%20Bollywood.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENicholas%20is%20a%20Christian%20man%2C%20divorced%2C%20playing%20up%20the%20facade%20of%20a%20casanova%20(he%20brags%20about%20how%20he%20would%20go%20on%20multiple%20dates%20every%20week)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20way%20to%20mask%20his%20drinking%20problem.%20Rajani%2C%20a%20headstrong%2C%20Hindu%20woman%2C%20in%20a%20steady%20relationship%20when%20she%20meets%20Nicholas%2C%20slowly%20begins%20to%20embrace%20the%20ease%20she%20feels%20around%20him.%20The%20surprise%20package%20of%20this%20segment%20is%20their%20cupid%20%E2%80%93%20Mandira%2C%20a%20devoted%2C%20visually-impaired%20listener%20for%20both%20Nick%20and%20Rajani%E2%80%99s%20programmes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inter-faith%20couple%20comes%20together%20despite%20opposition%20from%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20talks%20about%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98fairytale%E2%80%99%20was%20tested%20during%20Nicholas%E2%80%99%20periods%20of%20alcohol%20addiction.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20sombre%20moment%20that%20grounds%20the%20episode.%20When%20Nicholas%2C%20Rajani%20and%20their%20son%20Mahyaan%20pay%20a%20surprise%20visit%20to%20Mandira%20%E2%80%93%20a%20tearful%20reunion%20worthy%20of%20cameras%20%E2%80%93%20to%20Soni%E2%80%99s%20credit%2C%20he%20keeps%20rolling%20after%20they%20leave.%20After%20promising%20to%20%E2%80%98stay%20in%20touch%E2%80%99%2C%20Soni%20films%20the%20loneliness%20in%20Mandira%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20touching%20ode%20to%20those%20who%20magnanimously%20bat%20for%20love%2C%20even%20if%20they%20only%20have%20their%20solitude%20to%20live%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103116%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.43%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103116%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.43%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x457.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103116%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.43%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x134.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103116%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.29.43%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Love%20Storiyaan%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHomecoming%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShazia%20Iqbal%E2%80%99s%20episode%20about%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20couple%20eloping%20from%20Dhaka%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20in%20search%20of%20their%20happily-ever-after%20in%20Kolkata%20%E2%80%93%20is%20one%20of%20the%20finer%20episodes%20here.%20Their%20daughter%20recounts%20how%20Sunit%20and%20Farida%20moved%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20thinking%20they%20were%20going%20to%20a%20large-hearted%20country.%20However%2C%20the%20recent%20polarisation%20has%20evoked%20the%20images%20of%201973%20%E2%80%93%20the%20year%20Sunit%20and%20Farida%20had%20eloped%20from%20Dhaka%20%E2%80%93%20when%20they%20were%20surrounded%20by%20radicals%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIqbal%20touches%20upon%20the%20hardships%20the%20couple%20had%20to%20face%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20contrasting%20pictures%20of%20their%20youth%20and%20their%20weather-beaten%20faces%20today.%20Sunit%20came%20from%20a%20rich%20family%2C%20while%20Farida%20was%20from%20a%20politically%20influential%20family.%20Neither%20could%20have%20imagined%20a%20time%20when%20they%20would%20be%20struggling%20for%20basic%20necessities.%20To%20Iqbal%E2%80%99s%20credit%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20always%20their%20unconditional%20love%20of%20five%20decades.%20The%20episode%20follows%20Sunit%20and%20Farida%20going%20back%20to%20their%20homes%20in%20Chandpur%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20hardly%20picture-perfect.%20Sunit%E2%80%99s%20parents%20and%20his%20close%20relatives%20have%20all%20passed%2C%20while%20Farida%E2%80%99s%20brother%20is%20frozen%20through%20most%20of%20their%20first%20interaction.%20However%2C%20a%20text%20slide%20later%20tells%20us%20how%20the%20brother%20meets%20Farida%20and%20Sunit%2C%20and%20requests%20the%20crew%20to%20not%20film%20them.%20While%20it%20could%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98happy%20ending%E2%80%99%20the%20episode%20also%20draws%20focus%20to%20the%20pointlessness%20of%20the%20hurt%20and%20rage%20inflicted%20by%20people%20on%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERaah%20Sangharsh%20Ki%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkshay%20Indikar%E2%80%99s%20episode%20is%20my%20favourite%20one%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELove%20Storiyaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20how%20Utopian%20and%20idealistic%20it%20feels.%20Rahul%2C%20an%20IITian-turned-activist%20for%20adivasis%20meets%20Subhadra%2C%20a%20Dalit%20activist.%20Their%20common%20ground%20for%20social%20justice%20aside%2C%20they%20have%20very%20little%20in%20common.%20Rahul%20hails%20from%20a%20Brahmin%20family%20of%20engineers%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20something%20Subhadra%20knew%20nothing%20about%20when%20she%20agreed%20to%20marry%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndikar%E2%80%99s%20film%20benefits%20from%20Subhadra%E2%80%99s%20presence%20%E2%80%93%20a%20firecracker%20of%20a%20person%2C%20being%20matter-of-fact%20about%20her%20life%20and%20their%20relationship.%20Rahul%2C%20a%20man%20who%20speaks%20with%20sophistication%20and%20thought%2C%20almost%20comes%20off%20as%20the%20ideal%20partner.%20Hearing%20about%20where%20Subhadra%20began%2C%20and%20being%20witness%20to%20her%20personal%2C%20as%20well%20as%20academic%20growth%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20arcs%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20recently.%20Indikar%E2%80%99s%20film%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hide%20the%20fact%20that%20Rahul%20and%20Subhadra%E2%80%99s%20journey%20being%20rosy%20at%20all%20points%2C%20especially%20when%20Subhadra%20candidly%20confesses%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20had%20thoughts%20of%20leaving%20Rahul.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20I%20think%20%E2%80%93%20will%20I%20find%20anyone%20like%20him%3F%20Unlikely%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20a%20laugh.%20Seeing%20Subhadra%20find%20the%20vocabulary%20to%20voice%20her%20thoughts%20against%20patriarchy%20and%20caste%20bias%2C%20which%20has%20denied%20her%20so%20many%20opportunities%2C%20left%20me%20feeling%20giddy%20with%20its%20glimpse%20of%20what%20a%20just%20society%20would%20look%20like.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFaasle%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArchana%20Phadke%E2%80%99s%20episode%20about%20a%20Malayali%20woman%2C%20Dhanya%2C%20and%20an%20Afghan%20man%2C%20Homayon%2C%20meeting%20during%20college%20in%20the%20USSR%2C%20is%20visually%20the%20most%20refined%20one.%20This%20is%20a%20rare%20episode%2C%20where%20the%20re-enactments%20of%20Dhanya%20and%20Homayon%E2%80%99s%20anecdotes%20seem%20organic%2C%20especially%20with%20Homayon%20mentioning%20how%20he%20was%20reminded%20of%20Rekha%2C%20the%20first%20time%20he%20laid%20eyes%20on%20Dhanya%20outside%20their%20Dean%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20sheer%20logistics%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20argued%20that%20Dhanya%20and%20Homayon%E2%80%99s%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20rigorous%20love%20stories%20in%20the%20show.%20The%20couple%20recount%20how%20she%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20four%20years%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20to%20marry%20Homayon%2C%20who%20explicitly%20states%20that%20eloping%20was%20never%20an%20option%20like%20in%20the%20Bollywood%20movies.%20Shortly%20after%20they%20marry%2C%20Homayon%20is%20stranded%20in%20Taliban-ruled%20Afghanistan%2C%20causing%20Dhanya%20to%20follow%20him%20there%2C%20which%20meant%20a%20significant%20mortal%20risk.%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20poetic%20how%20following%20her%20husband%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20oppressive%20environments%20for%20women%20on%20earth%20also%20becomes%20her%20key%20to%20lifelong%20freedom%20and%20equitable%20companionship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELove%20Beyond%20Labels%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20love%20story%20between%20transwoman%20Tista%20and%20transman%20Dipan%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20ground%20to%20cover%20in%20about%2030%20mins%2C%20but%20Colin%20D%E2%80%99Cunha%20does%20well%20to%20take%20us%20through%20the%20beats.%20Tista%2C%20assigned%20male%20at%20birth%2C%20found%20herself%20drawn%20towards%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esindoor%20khela%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20a%20ritual%20for%20married%20women%20to%20conclude%20Durga%20Puja%20festivities.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Dipan%20found%20himself%20drawn%20to%20sports%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20shirts.%20Growing%20up%20with%20shame%20in%20conservative%20localities%2C%20both%20Tista%20and%20Dipan%20talk%20about%20their%20struggles%2C%20periods%20of%20self-loathing%2C%20and%20finding%20peace%20with%20their%20identities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20sharp%20touch%20from%20D%E2%80%99Cunha%2C%20when%20Tista%20is%20recounting%20how%20neighbours%20would%20complain%20to%20her%20mother%20about%20her.%20She%20sighs%20saying%20she%20would%20feel%20bothered%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20soon%20go%20back%20to%20acting%20like%20her%20favourite%20heroine.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fine%2C%20irreverent%20moment%20puncturing%20all%20the%20trauma%20out%20of%20the%20picture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20moments%20in%20D%E2%80%99Cunha%E2%80%99s%20episode%20that%20feel%20staged%2C%20and%20voiceovers%20that%20take%20us%20out%20of%20the%20story.%20However%2C%20the%20Dharma%20aesthetic%20is%20most%20prominent%20here%20%5Bin%20a%20good%20way%5D%2C%20and%20if%20this%20has%20to%20be%20the%20gateway%20to%20sensitise%20the%20Indian%20middle-class%20about%20the%20trans%20community%2C%20then%20D%E2%80%99Cunha%20and%20his%20crew%20should%20consider%20themselves%20successful.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708060019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16103209%2FScreenshot-2024-02-16-at-10.30.13%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Flove-storiyaan-the-series-is-proof-that-love-conquers-all-even-middling-craft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20hurts%20the%20six-episode%20show%20is%20its%20brisk%2025-35%20minutes%20runtime%20per%20episode%2C%20which%20results%20in%20complex%20issues%20being%20magically%20resolved%20or%20narrative%20lighthouses%20appearing%20out%20of%20nowhere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2F