e%20arm%20to%20the%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20the%20need%20for%20the%20regrouping%20of%20democratic%20forces%20was%20never%20more%20urgent%20and%20obvious.%20The%20objective%20conditions%20for%20a%20democratic%20%E2%80%9Cresistance%E2%80%9D%20are%20all%20too%20evident.%20All%20that%20is%20needed%20is%20for%20the%20non-BJP%20leaders%20across%20the%20country%20to%20understand%20the%20stakes%20involved%20and%20to%20revive%20in%20earnest%20the%20%E2%80%9Copposition%20unity%E2%80%9D%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%20to%20the%20perennial%20question%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20to%20be%20done%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20that%20Lenin%20once%20posed%20is%20simple%3A%20devise%20a%20tool-kit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20a%20possible%20draft%20should%20look%20like.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EVision%20and%20Values%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20recommitting%20ourselves%20to%20a%20strong%2C%20stable%20and%20powerful%20India%2C%20we%20place%20the%20highest%20premium%20on%20the%20preservation%20and%20strengthening%C2%A0%20of%20provisions%20and%20principles%20of%20a%20democratic%2C%20plural%2C%20federal%20and%20socially%20harmonious%20political%20system%2C%20as%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMission%20Statement%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20mobilise%20the%20masses%20in%20a%20mutually%20reinforcing%20and%20beneficial%2C%20coordinated%20approach%20so%20as%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20verdict%20reflects%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20sentiments%20and%20aspirations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EStrategic%20Objective%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20dislodge%20the%20BJP%2F%20Sangh%20Parivar%20from%20its%20authoritarian%20perch%20and%20restore%20to%20governance%20a%20democratic%20and%20collaborative%20temper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EParameters%20and%20co-ordinates%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20withstanding%20the%20self-serving%20claims%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%2C%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20command%20a%20majority%20of%20Hindu%20votes%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20favoured%20by%20all%20minorities%20and%20other%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20the%20society%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOutside%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20and%20the%20western%20states%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20distinctly%20vulnerable%20and%20its%20acceptance%20is%20extremely%20thin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20popularity%20and%20acceptance%20is%20over-hyped%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20%E2%80%9Cabsence%E2%80%9D%20of%20an%20all-India%20opposition%20figure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAlliance%20Calculus%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20ensure%20that%20the%20anti-BJP%20vote%20does%20get%20divided%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20garner%20all%20the%20anti-incumbency%20votes%20in%20states%20where%20non-BJP%20parties%20are%20in%20power%3B%20after%20all%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20the%20only%20party%20that%20has%20the%20experience%20of%20winning%20or%20losing%20elections.%20Political%20acumen%20and%20imagination%20are%20not%20the%20monopoly%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejodi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20must%20follow%2C%20that%20an%20electoral%20alliance%20among%20all%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20is%20not%20an%20end%20itself%3B%20rather%2C%20the%20primary%20purpose%20of%20the%20alliance%20is%20to%20find%20the%20creativity%20and%20imagination%20at%20the%20local%2Fconstituency%20level%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20BJP%20loses%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Deng%20Xiaoping%20axiom%2C%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20which%20party%20wins%20as%20long%20as%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20get%20the%20seat.%C2%A0%20There%20cannot%20be%20any%20doubt%20as%20to%20who%20is%20the%20principal%20%E2%80%9Cenemy%E2%80%9D%20and%20his%20defeat%20has%20to%20be%20the%20one%20and%20only%20consideration.%C2%A0%20A%20brutal%20clarity%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20to%20be%20done%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20begin%20with%2C%20a%20joint%20statement%20of%20purpose%2C%20with%20a%20few%20specific%20promises%2C%20from%20all%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20and%20leaders%2C%20should%20kick-start%20the%20process.%20The%20idea%20should%20be%20to%20make%20it%20clear%20how%20the%20democratic%20forces%20differ%20from%20the%20Modi-led%20coalition%20of%20vested%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20here%20are%20a%20few%20suggestions%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EPromise%20to%20respect%20the%20neutrality%20and%20professional%20ethos%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EUndertake%20to%20restore%20constitutional%20institutions%20to%20their%20vital%20selves%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EDeclare%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20hold%20a%20press%20conference%20every%20six%20months%3B%20and%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20will%20attend%20parliament%20regularly%2C%20and%20answer%20questions%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20clearly%20that%20the%20media%20will%20not%20be%20subjected%20to%20arm-twisting%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20misuse%20of%20federal%20agencies%20for%20political%20purposes%20would%20be%20stopped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EFederal%20principles%20and%20practices%20will%20be%20followed%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20cooperation%20and%20accommodation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20tool-kit%20and%20its%20contents%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBitterness%20and%20bad%20blood%20in%20the%20sharing%20of%20seats%20should%20be%20put%20behind%3B%20instead%2C%20national%20leaders%20should%20direct%20their%20district%20level%20party%20leaders%2Factivists%20to%20organise%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esammelans%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20there%20could%20be%20an%20exchange%20of%20ideas%2C%20experiences%2C%20resources%20and%20insights%20on%20how%20not%20to%20allow%20the%20BJP%20(with%20or%20without%20acts%20of%20omission%20or%20commission%20by%20the%20EC%20)%20to%20manipulate%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20would%20be%20need%20to%20hold%20join%20training%20and%20orientation%20camps%2C%20where%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20list%20is%20diligently%20examined%3B%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20must%20be%20ensured%20that%20all%20genuine%20voters%20actually%20get%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise.%20There%20have%20been%20disquieting%20reports%20of%20how%20in%20BJP-ruled%20states%20Muslim%20voters%20are%20impeded%20on%20voting%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbove%20all%2C%20the%20alliance%20leaders%20would%20need%20to%20appreciate%20the%20indispensability%20of%20creating%20an%20image%20of%20a%20purposefully%20united%20democratic%20phalanx.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20hold%20joint%20rallies%20and%20press%20conferences%2C%20they%20must%20direct%20and%20inspire%20their%20district%2Fconstituency%20level%20cadres%20and%20activists%20to%20work%20together.%20An%20understanding%20among%20the%20top%20leaders%20does%20not%20necessarily%20and%20automatically%20produce%20synergy%20at%20the%20district%20level.%20This%20habit%20of%20pooling%20resources%2C%20energies%20and%20experiences%20at%20the%20local%20level%20needs%20to%20be%20assiduously%20attended%20to.%C2%A0%3C%