ch%20lasted%20for%20six%20hours%20till%201.30%20am%2C%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20gave%20our%20commitment%20to%20dialogue%20during%20the%20meeting%20but%20strongly%20objected%20against%20the%20excess%20use%20of%20police%20force%20on%20our%20protesting%20farmers.%20We%20told%20the%20central%20ministers%20that%20we%20are%20not%20from%20Pakistan.%20We%20want%20solution%2C%20not%20confrontation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-%20political)%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20the%20protests%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20while%20farmers%20were%20fully%20determined%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%2C%20they%20would%20wait%20for%20the%20outcome%20of%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20talks%20fail%20on%20that%20day%2C%20we%20will%20go%20ahead.%20But%20till%20that%20time%20we%20will%20maintain%20status%20quo%20and%20expect%20security%20forces%20to%20adopt%20restraint%20and%20avoid%20any%20shelling%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20barrier%20where%20our%20farmers%20are%20camping%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-at-shambhu-barrier-vow-not-to-return-until-centre-enacts-a-law-on-msp%5C%22%3EFarmers%20at%20Shambhu%20Barrier%20Vow%20Not%20to%20Return%20Until%20Centre%20Enacts%20a%20Law%20on%20MSP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20chief%20minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20also%20raised%20the%20matter%20on%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20in%20three%20districts%20of%20Punjab%20bordering%20Haryana%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20caused%20problems%20for%20students%20who%20had%20to%20write%20exams%20and%20affected%20normal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMann%20said%20such%20a%20move%20was%20not%20necessary%20when%20farmers%20were%20camping%20peacefully.%20He%20asked%20the%20U